Before creating, modifying, or reviewing any component or stories file under
`src/cakeand/components/`, read and follow the full skill at
[.claude/skills/storybook-component-docs/SKILL.md](../../.claude/skills/storybook-component-docs/SKILL.md).

It defines the mandatory rules: CSS custom-property tokens only
(`--color-*`, `--space-*`, `--radius-*`, `--stroke-*`, `--type-*`), the
docs-page section order (intro · theming · behavior · Usage · Design tokens
used · Accessibility · Do/Don't), the canonical story order ending in an
AllVariants matrix, argTypes rules (`control: false`, never
`table.disable` except `ref`), `['!autodocs']` on pure interaction tests,
and the verification steps. Canonical exemplar:
`src/cakeand/components/Button/`.
